data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is conveniently located to everything Youngsville has to offer. The spacious living area features a wood burning/gas fireplace and a large window overlooking the patio and backyard. The updated kitchen offers granite countertops and stainless appliances. Adjacent to the kitchen is the dining room which features a wood accent wall and more windows allowing in lots of natural light. The primary bedroom has a large walk in closet and private bath with granite countertops, double vanities, separate shower and garden tub. There is a flex space in the hall near the extra bedrooms and second bath that's perfect for a desk. Trane AC/Heat unit installed in June 2019 and water heater installed in January 2023. The private backyard is fenced and has a storage building. Call for your showing today!
